name: Windows 11 Mockup  by Presently
description:
Windows 11 mockup is a containing different frame created to give you the all-new Windows 11 feel.

In this mockup pack, you will find


Light Modes

  • The official windows wallpaper
  • Original pastel color for the windows 11 with bubbles around it
  • Pastel colors without Bubbles
  • Sky blue, Orange, and red pastel colors
  • Patterned shapes with different orange shades


Dark Modes

  • Original windows 11 dark mode wallpaper
  • Original dark scene color for the windows 11 with bubbles around it
  • Original pastel color for the windows 11
  • 2 Right orientation mockup
  • 2 Left orientation mockup
